<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1203065>
    dc:description "FIGURE 56. Caligus seriolicolus nom. nov. female. A. habitus, dorsal; B, posterior part of genital complex, ventral view showingfifth legsand flattened ventral lobes concealing oviductopenings; C, antennaand post-antennal process, drawn insitu; D, leg 1 with anterior process arrowed; E, leg 3. Scale bars:1 mm on A, 0.5 mm on B, 200 µm on C–E." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1203065/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

